## Оформить заказ [/supplier/places/{id}/order]        
+ Parameters
    + id: `1` (number, required) - идентификатор заведения
    
### Заказ [POST]

+ Request (application/json)


        {
            "serveDate" : "2015-08-05T09:40:51.620Z",
            "order" : [
                {
                    "id"    : 2,
                    "name"  : "Капучино",
                    "price" : 100.50
                },
                {
                    "id"    : 2,
                    "name"  : "Капучино",
                    "price" : 100.50
                },
                {
                    "id"    : 3,
                    "name"  : "Сэндвич с курицей",
                    "price" : 200.00
                }
            ]
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /supplier/places/{id}/order/1

    + Body

            {
                "id"        : 1,
                "orderDate" : "2015-08-05T08:40:51.620Z",
                "ticket"    : "12FA4",
                "total"     : 400.10
            }
